metadata.name: ANGEL #1
metadata.description:
ELYSIAN CHAINS is a sci-fi story that delves in the complexities of life, relationships, and the pursuit of dreams.

Play the game at http://elysianchains.com/ Twitter: @elysianchains New content is added weekly. 

Mint Collection 00 - A Bored Angel's Thesis: Explore the epic journey of Angel of Creation as they struggle to find meaning and purpose in a universe they created trillions of years ago. Within the celestial realms of the Noise, Angels must now confront their own boredom and temptation as they search for meaning in their own existence.
